snippet.title: 遅れた宿題 Late Homework - Find your missing homework scattered throughout a haunted school!
snippet.description:
Download for free on itch.io https://sodaraptor.itch.io/late-homework?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt Haneko has forgotten her assigned homework and left them at school, and they're due tomorrow.

Feeling she has no choice, she decides her only way to avoid failing the semester is to make a trip back to school at night and retrieve the assignments. But something's not right in the building...

an anomaly lurks the halls.
